  "title": "Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Highlights</strong></u></p><p>· Medical Benefit</p><p>· Monday to Friday – 9am to 6pm (5 days/week)</p><p>· Transport pickup/drop off near MRT station</p><p>· Lunch and Tea break provided<br /></p><p></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>- Record and report work injuries, work medic cases, etc. to MOM (iReport) and liaise with insurance agency</p><p>- Apply for worker passes (Jurong Port, Jurong Island, PSA, etc.) as needed</p><p>- Manage uniform, safety boots, and other supplies issuance and records</p><p>- Track daily weight amounts and prepare reports</p><p>- Arrange office/workshop meals and prepare monthly reports for Accounts</p><p>- Handle documentation, filing, and office supplies</p><p>- Assist with IT, building, and other administrative issues</p><p>- Respond to authority agent enquiries/inspections</p><p>- Answer phone calls, attend to visitors, and perform daily admin duties</p><p>- Prepare sponsorships, festival gifts for customers and staff, and other tasks as assigned</p><p></p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>- Diploma or above with 2-3 years of relevant experience</p><p>- Able to communicate with diverse nationalities</p><p>- Positive attitude, team player, and able to work under pressure</p><p>- Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Word</p><p> </p>",
